   "konu": "02 - K\ufffdT\ufffdBU'L-\ufffdM\ufffdN",
   "numara": 1,
   "metin": "\n\u003cdiv align=\"left\"\u003e\n\t\u003ctable border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" dir=\"ltr\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-width: 0px\"\u003e\n\t\t\u003ctbody\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctd valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: none; border-width: medium\"\u003e\n\u003ch3 style=\"text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" color=\"#FF0000\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\u003ca name=\"_Toc64733193\"\u003e1- \ufffdm\ufffdn Ve \u003c/a\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color:#FF9900\"\u003ePeygamber\u003c/span\u003ein: \ufffd\ufffdsl\ufffdm be\ufffd \ufffdey \ufffdzerine bina \nedilmi\ufffdtir\ufffd... Kavli\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\ufffdm\ufffdn, dil ile s\ufffdylemek ve \norganlarla i\ufffdlemektir. \ufffdm\ufffdn, artar ve eksilir. Y\ufffdce Allah \ufffd\ufffdyle buyurdu:\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003e\u0026#34;O, \nm\ufffd\u0026#39;minlerin y\ufffdreklerine, \ufffdm\ufffdnlar\ufffdn\ufffd kat kat art\ufffdrmalar\ufffd i\ufffdin sek\ufffdneti indirendir\u003c/span\u003e\u0026#34;\n\u003c/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(Feth: 48/4)\u003c/span\u003e\u003csub\u003e;\u003c/sub\u003e\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003e\u0026#34;Biz de \nonlar\ufffdn hid\ufffdyetini art\ufffdrm\ufffd\ufffdt\ufffdk\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(Kehf: \n18/13)\u003c/span\u003e;\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003e\u0026#34;Allah \nhid\ufffdyeti kabul edenlerin hid\ufffdyetini art\ufffdr\ufffdr\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/b\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(Meryem: 19/76)\u003c/span\u003e;\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003e\n\u0026#34;Hid\ufffdyeti kabul edenler \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(e gelince\u003cb\u003e)\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003e, \nonlar\ufffdn muvaffak\ufffdyetini art\ufffdrm\ufffd\ufffd, onlara takvalar\ufffdn\ufffd ilh\ufffdm etmi\ufffdtir\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(Muhammed: 47/17)\u003c/span\u003e;\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003e\u0026#34;\ufffdm\ufffdn \nedenlerin de \ufffdm\ufffdnlar\ufffd arts\ufffdn\ufffd\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(Muddessir: 74/31)\u003c/span\u003e;\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003eVe Allah\u0026#39;\ufffdn \ufffdu kavli:\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\u003ca name=\"_Toc64733125\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003e\u0026#34;Bir s\ufffdre indirildi\ufffdi zaman i\ufffdlerinden kimi: Bu s\ufffdre \nhanginizin \ufffdm\ufffdn\ufffdn\ufffd art\ufffdrd\ufffd, der. \ufffdm\ufffdn etmi\ufffd olanlara gelince \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(her inen s\ufffdre)\u003c/span\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003e \nd\ufffdima onlar\ufffdn \ufffdm\ufffdn\ufffdn\ufffd art\ufffdrm\ufffd\ufffdt\ufffdr ve onlar birbirleriyle m\ufffdjdele\ufffdirler.\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color:blue\"\u003e(Tevbe: 9/124)\u003c/span\u003e\u003csub\u003e;\u003c/sub\u003e\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003eVe zikri cel\ufffdl olan Allah\u0026#39;\ufffdn \ufffdu \nkavli:\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003e\u0026#34;Onlar \n\ufffdyle kimselerdir ki halk kendilerine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e\n(D\ufffd\ufffdmanlar\ufffdn\ufffdz olan)\u003c/span\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003e insanlar size kar\ufffd\ufffd ordu \nhaz\ufffdrlad\ufffdlar, o h\ufffdlde onlardan korkun, dedi de, bu\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(s\ufffdz)\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003e \u003cb\u003e\nonlar\ufffdn \ufffdm\ufffdn\ufffdn\ufffd art\ufffdrd\ufffd ve: Allah bize yeter, o ne g\ufffdzel vekildir, dediler\u0026#34;\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(\ufffdli \ufffdmr\ufffdn: 9/173)\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003eVe Y\ufffdce \nAllah\u0026#39;\ufffdn \ufffdu kavli:\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003e\n\u0026#34;M\ufffd\u0026#39;minler d\ufffd\ufffdman ordular\ufffdn\ufffd g\ufffdr\ufffdnce: \ufffd\ufffdte bu Allah\u0026#39;\ufffdn ve Ras\ufffdl\ufffd\u0026#39;n\ufffdn bize va\u0026#39;d \netti\ufffdi \ufffdeydir. Allah ve Ras\ufffdl\ufffd do\ufffdru s\ufffdylemi\ufffdtir, dediler. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(Bu)\u003c/span\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003e onlar\ufffdn \n\ufffdm\ufffdnlar\ufffdn\ufffd ve teslimiyetlerini art\ufffdrmaktan ba\ufffdka bir \ufffdey yapmad\ufffd\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(Ahz\ufffdb: 33/22)\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003eAllah \ni\ufffdin \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(y\ufffdni Allah\u0026#39;a t\ufffdat sebebiyle)\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e \nsevmek ve\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003eAllah i\ufffdin sevmemek \ufffdm\ufffdndand\ufffdr.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003eOmer ibn \nAbdilaz\ufffdz \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(101)\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e, \nAdiyy ibn Adiyy \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(123)\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e\u0026#39;e\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e\ufffd\ufffdyle yazd\ufffd: Muhakkak ki \ufffdm\ufffdn\ufffdn bir tak\ufffdm farizalar\ufffd,\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003eakideleri, men\u0026#39; edilmi\ufffd \ufffdeyleri ve mend\ufffdblar\ufffd vard\ufffdr.\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003eKim bunlar\ufffd tam yaparsa \ufffdm\ufffdn\ufffd tamamlam\ufffd\ufffd olur.\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003eKim de bu i\ufffdleri tam yapmazsa \ufffdm\ufffdn\ufffd kem\ufffdle\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003eerdirmemi\ufffd olur. E\ufffder ben ya\ufffdarsam, bu i\ufffdleri\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003ebilmeniz i\ufffdin ben onlar\ufffd size iyice bey\ufffdn edip\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003ea\ufffd\ufffdklayaca\ufffd\ufffdm. Ve \ufffdayet \ufffdl\ufffdrsem, ben sizlere\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003ehem-dem ve y\ufffdr olmaya h\ufffdrsl\ufffd de\ufffdilim.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e\ufffdbr\ufffdh\ufffdm \naleyhi\u0026#39;s-sel\ufffdm da\u003cb\u003e:\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cb\u003e \ufffd\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003eEy Rabb\u0026#39;im, \n\ufffdl\ufffdleri nas\ufffdl diriltece\ufffdini bana g\ufffdster, dedi; Allah: inanmad\ufffdn m\ufffd yoksa dedi; O \nda: \ufffdnand\ufffdm, fakat \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(g\ufffdz\ufffdmle de g\ufffdrerek)\u003c/span\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003e \nkalbimin yat\ufffd\ufffdmas\ufffd i\ufffdin\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003e\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(Bakara: 2/260)\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"color:\nblack\"\u003edemi\ufffdti.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003eMu\ufffdz ibn \nCebel \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(18)\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e, \nbir z\ufffdta: Bizimle otur da \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(d\ufffdn i\ufffdlerini \nm\ufffdz\ufffdkere ederek)\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e bir s\ufffdat \ufffdm\ufffdn\ufffd art\ufffdral\ufffdm, \ndedi.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e\ufffdbn \nMes\u0026#39;\ufffdd \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(32)\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e: \nYak\ufffdn, \ufffdm\ufffdn\ufffdn tam\ufffdm\ufffdd\ufffdr, dedi.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e\ufffdbn Omer\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(73)\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e: Kul, \ng\ufffdnl\ufffdndeki \ufffd\ufffdbhe veren \ufffdeyleri\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003etam\ufffdmiyle terk \netmedik\ufffde takvan\ufffdn hak\ufffdkatine\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003eula\ufffdmaz, dedi.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003eMuc\ufffdhid \nibn Cebr \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(101)\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e,\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color:red\"\u003eD\ufffdnden Nuh\u0026#39;a \ntavsiye etti\ufffdini sizin i\ufffdin de bir \ufffderiat yapt\ufffd\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color:black\"\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color:blue\"\u003e(\ufffd\ufffdr\ufffd: 42/13)\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan style=\"color:black\"\u003e\n\ufffdyetini:\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003eEy Muhammed, sana da Nuh\u0026#39;a da bir tek \ndin tavsiye\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003eettik, demektir diye tefs\ufffdr etti.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 33pt; line-height: 19pt; margin: 7pt\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cfont face=\"Verdana\" style=\"font-size: 10pt\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e\ufffdbn \nAbbas, \u003c/span\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: red\"\u003e\u0026#34;Sizden her biriniz i\ufffdin bir \ufffderiat, \nbir yol ta\u0026#39;y\ufffdn ettik\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: blue\"\u003e(M\ufffdide: 5/48)\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e\n\ufffdyetindeki \u003c/span\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color:red\"\u003e\u0026#34;\ufffd\ufffdr\u0026#39;a ve minh\ufffdc\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e\ufffd, \ngeni\ufffd yol ve s\ufffdnnet\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003ediye tefs\ufffdr etti. Yine \ufffdbn \nAbb\ufffds, \u003cb\u003e\u0026#34;\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color:red\"\u003eDuan\ufffdz olmasayd\ufffd Rabb\u0026#39;im size \nde\ufffder verir miydi de\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003e\n\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color:blue\"\u003e(Furkan: 25/77)\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan style=\"color:black\"\u003e\nkel\ufffdm\ufffd\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003esebebiyle, du\ufffdn\ufffdz \ufffdm\ufffdn\ufffdn\ufffdz demektir, \ndiye tefs\ufffdr etti.\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan style=\"color: black\"\u003eDu\ufffdn\ufffdn l\ufffdgatteki ma\u0026#39;n\ufffds\ufffd \n\ufffdm\ufffdnd\ufffdr.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/font\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\u003c/tbody\u003e\u003c/table\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n"
  },
  {
